text: Hinnak yahuudey isin woo Aracal Sugteenii?Nabii Yaq-qhuubuh Rabi yemeete waqdiy isi xaylo kobxiseeh Anu Rabek lakal maca Aqbudettoonuu keenik iyye waqdi?Ä¶u-Yallaay, ku- Abbobti Nabii Ibraahimiiy Nabii Ismaaqil kee Nabii Iscaaqh Yalla Aqbudenno usuk inki Yallah Anuk nanu kaa inkittoyseeh kaah yuqunxee marah Anuk iyyen
